==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*θεράπων / therapōn / ther-ap'-ohn

===Etymology===
*Apparently a participle from an otherwise obsolete derivation of the base of [[θέρος]] {{GG|2330}};

===Noun===
'''θεράπων'''

# a menial attendant (as if cherishing): - [[servant]].

